overview: The staff of RF VIDEO was blown away with our latest shoot interview. We knew going in this man would pull no punches, as he is known in locker rooms across the country as a straight shooter. We’ve followed his career from SMW to ECW to finally WWE and yet we still weren’t prepared for what we caught on tape. That’s right, RF VIDEO is proud to announce the latest in our exclusive line of shoot interviews featuring the one and only AL SNOW!
title: RFVideo Shoot: Al Snow 2008
